{"id": "art-462", "label": "Art. 462", "title": "Art. 462: Soluţiile după rejudecare", "slug": "art-462", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_935378685\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1456\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_935378685\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 462: Solu&#355;iile\ndup&#259; rejudecare </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1353225675\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1455\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1353225675\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; se constat&#259; c&#259; cererea de revizuire\neste întemeiat&#259;, instan&#355;a anuleaz&#259; hot&#259;rârea, în\nm&#259;sura în care a fost admis&#259; revizuirea, sau hot&#259;rârile care nu\nse pot concilia &#351;i pronun&#355;&#259; o nou&#259; hot&#259;râre potrivit\ndispozi&#355;iilor art. 395-399, care se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_579227891\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1454\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_579227891\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Instan&#355;a rejudec&#259; cauza prin extindere &#351;i\ncu privire la p&#259;r&#355;ile care nu au formulat cerere de revizuire, putând\nhot&#259;rî &#351;i în privin&#355;a lor, f&#259;r&#259; s&#259; le poat&#259;\ncrea acestora o situa&#355;ie mai grea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_801438964\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1453\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_801438964\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Instan&#355;a ia m&#259;suri pentru restabilirea\nsitua&#355;iei anterioare, dispunând, dac&#259; este cazul, restituirea amenzii\npl&#259;tite &#351;i a bunurilor confiscate, a cheltuielilor judiciare pe care\ncel în favoarea c&#259;ruia s-a admis revizuirea nu era &#355;inut s&#259; le\nsuporte sau alte asemenea m&#259;suri.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_850783532\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1452\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_850783532\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dac&#259; instan&#355;a constat&#259; c&#259; cererea de\nrevizuire este neîntemeiat&#259;, o respinge &#351;i dispune obligarea\nrevizuientului la plata cheltuielilor judiciare c&#259;tre stat, precum &#351;i\nreluarea execut&#259;rii pedepsei, în cazul în care aceasta a fost\nsuspendat&#259;.</span></p>"}